  "detailed_description": "You are trapped inside your worst nightmare... School! in an endless loop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/694b5737e62309b0d27bf4ce0c97364a.poster.avif?t=1723926745\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/694b5737e62309b0d27bf4ce0c97364a.webm?t=1723926745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/694b5737e62309b0d27bf4ce0c97364a.mp4?t=1723926745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rules of the game</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find anomalies (Don't overlook any anomaly)<br></li><li>If you do find any anomaly, turn back! Some anomalies have specific interactions to escape them successfully.<br></li><li>If you don't find any anomaly, do not turn back.<br></li><li>Find 10 consecutive anomalies to exit.</li></ul><br><strong>Tenfold Loop</strong> is a short walking simulator where the player is trapped inside an endless loop. The only way to finish the game is to find <strong>10 consecutives anomalies</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/667426d8e580203af6582eeb57f2972f.poster.avif?t=1723926745\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/667426d8e580203af6582eeb57f2972f.webm?t=1723926745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2876800/extras/667426d8e580203af6582eeb57f2972f.mp4?t=1723926745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
